end_situation
Disk World creator help
end_situation

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
end_situation -  Ends a situation previously added and started on the room that is managed by this object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void end_situation(int num,
object room)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^num%^RESET%^ - number labelling the situation
%^BOLD%^room%^RESET%^ - room to end situation on
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/multiroom_situation_changer.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Ends a situation previously added and started on the room
that is managed by this object.
These situations can be invoked manually with start_situation 
or automatically via automate_situations. 
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_situation, start_situation, automate_situations

.EP

